                            <comment id="15848152" author="blerer" created="Wed, 1 Feb 2017 09:06:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;An &lt;tt&gt;UPDATE&lt;/tt&gt; or a &lt;tt&gt;DELETE&lt;/tt&gt; query with an empty &lt;tt&gt;IN&lt;/tt&gt; restriction will result in an invalid mutation that we be send to the replicas.&lt;br/&gt;
The patch makes sure that if an &lt;tt&gt;UPDATE&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;DELETE&lt;/tt&gt; query contains an empty &lt;tt&gt;IN&lt;/tt&gt; restriction no mutation will be created.&lt;/p&gt;

